	&lt;li&gt;It is&lt;strong&gt; India&amp;#39;s first and largest aerospace research firm&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The primary aim of NAL is to develop civilian aircraft in India.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The current director is NAL is&lt;strong&gt; Dr. Abhay Pashilkar&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
