&lt;p&gt;A &lt;strong&gt;Biosphere Reserve&lt;/strong&gt; is a unique and representative ecosystem of terrestrial and coastal areas which are internationally recognized within the framework of UNESCO&amp;#39;s Man and Biosphere (MAB) Programme.&lt;/p&gt;

